WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:11.250 --> 00:00:17.708
 Hi, my name is Lili, I told you a part of my great adventure with the Bear. 

00:00:18.353 --> 00:00:21.579
 But the greatest adventure was adolescence. 

00:00:23.920 --> 00:00:26.700
 And not mine, obviously. 

00:00:27.080 --> 00:00:29.360
 adolescence 

00:00:30.630 --> 00:00:35.130
 One day, I noticed that my friend started growing up. 

00:00:35.524 --> 00:00:38.341
 And it was not just the hair that was starting to grow here and there. 

00:00:38.634 --> 00:00:39.827
 He was always ... 

00:00:40.182 --> 00:00:41.365
 You see ... a little hairier. 

00:00:44.640 --> 00:00:48.520
 And I'm not talking about his size. That, I already noticed. 

00:00:50.100 --> 00:00:51.824
 But he became irritable, 

00:00:52.159 --> 00:00:53.189
 anxious about his appearance, 

00:00:55.285 --> 00:00:56.916
 always frustrated etc. 

00:01:30.980 --> 00:01:32.920
 It was a nightmare. 

00:01:33.808 --> 00:01:35.087
 I loved him so much 

00:01:35.529 --> 00:01:37.208
 and I knew that I had to be patient 

00:01:37.666 --> 00:01:39.125
 and indulgent. 

00:01:55.278 --> 00:01:58.000
 Unfortunately, it was sometimes difficult. 

00:02:13.211 --> 00:02:15.541
 He always asked for forgiveness 

00:02:16.914 --> 00:02:17.541
 but I noticed 

00:02:18.126 --> 00:02:19.000
 that some things 

00:02:19.652 --> 00:02:21.291
 have changed. 

00:02:56.303 --> 00:02:58.298
 Yet we continued to love each other 

00:02:58.661 --> 00:03:00.291
 and we worked a lot on our relationship. 

00:03:10.569 --> 00:03:13.250
 During the therapy, he hardly spoke but 

00:03:13.811 --> 00:03:16.541
 he always found a way to express himself. 

00:03:24.116 --> 00:03:27.616
 I could not be angry for a long time, 

00:03:28.249 --> 00:03:30.289
 he always knew how to make me laugh. 

